      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Deuteronomy 17:18",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ",) and to govern himself and his kingdom by it; the law of God being frequently and most properly called ",
        "children": []
