        "class": "ital",
        "text": "a testimony, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "because it is a witness of God’s will, and man’s duty. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "They made him king, and anointed him ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "— As was wont to be done in doubtful cases, when there was any competition or question about the crown, as now there was.",
        "children": []
